Task3: (name<space>float)

collect three strings from user  name<space>float

string1: "ravi 10.30"  
string2: "meghala 12.19"
string3: "Gokul 20.20"

split + indexing

10.30 + 12.19 + 20.20 ===> output ===> round (42.69000) 5 decimal places should be (format)
string1=input('Enter string1(name<space>float):')
string2=input('Enter string2(name<space>float):')
string3=input('Enter string3(name<space>float):')
str1=string1.split()
str2=string2.split()
str3=string3.split()
output=float(str1[1])+float(str2[1])+float(str3[1])
print(round(output))
