task3:
3. Write a Python program to print the first and last index where a given character appears in a string.
Input:
Enter the string: communication
Enter the character to search: c
Expected Output:
First occurrence at index: 0
Last occurrence at index: 7

string=input('Enter the string:')  #communication
search_char=input('Enter the character to search:')  #c
length=len(string)
indexx=0
count=0
for i in string:
    if i==search_char:
        string_index=string.index(i,indexx,length)
        if count==0:
            print('First occurrence at index:',string_index)
        indexx+=1
        count+=1
        if count==:
            print('last occurrence at index:',string_index)
else:
    print(count)

